content:
Add Contract Line Items to Service Contracts

Set up contract line items to specify which products a service contract covers. Contract line items only display on the Contract Line Items related list on service contracts (not on contracts!). You can only use contract line items if your Salesforce org uses products.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To set up service contracts and contract line items with entitlements:	
Manage Entitlements
Customize Application

NOTE Entitlements must be enabled in your org for you to set up contract line items.

From the object management settings for contract line items:
Customize contract line item fields.
Customize contract line item page layouts.
Customize other objects' page layouts.
Set field-level security on contract line items.
Set field history tracking on contract line items.

SEE ALSO
Entitlement Management Setup Checklist
title: Set Up Contract Line Items in Service Cloud
